{"results":[{"aya":"022","id":3810,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你们应当集合不义者和他们的伴侣，以及他们舍真主而崇拜的，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"023","id":3811,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"然后指示他们火狱的道路，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"024","id":3812,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"并拦住他们，因为他们的确要受审问。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"025","id":3813,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你们怎么不互助呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"026","id":3814,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"不然！他们在今日是归顺的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"027","id":3815,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"于是他们大家走向前来，互相谈论，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"028","id":3816,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"这些人说：你们确已用权力胁迫我们。","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-3.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-5.json"}}